Fourth Department,

July, 1977

(July 12, 1977) Dennis Darling, an Infant, by Wanda Darling, His Mother and Natural Guardian, et al., Appellants, v Zippo Manufacturing Co. Inc. et al., Respondents.

Appeal unanimously dismissed, without costs, upon stipulation. (Appeal from judgment of Erie Supreme Court—negligence.) Present —Cardamone, J. P., Simons, Dillon, Goldman and Witmer, JJ.
